OL,3,CKatie Simpson Ombudsman report
OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FUTV has seen parts of a Police
OL,7,FOmbudsman Report into the death of Co
OL,8,FArmagh show jumper Katie Simpson in
OL,9,F2020.
OL,11,FThe 21 year old died after an incident
OL,12,Fat a property in Gortnessy Medaows on
OL,13,Fthe 3 August.
OL,15,FHer sister's long term partner
OL,16,FJonathan Creswell was charged with
OL,17,FKatie's murder and rape in 2021.
OL,19,FThe 36 year old was dead at home 24
OL,20,Fhours after the trial started back in
OL,21,FApril this year.
