OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FConcerns were raised by her family and
OL,7,Ffriends into the initial police
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FFrom the extracts UTV has seen the
OL,11,FOmbudsman found a number of police
OL,12,Ffailures and missed opportunities.
