OL,3,CKatie Simpson Ombudsman report
OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FIt found "responding officers in
OL,7,Fparticular failed to adopt an
OL,8,Finvestigative mindset...Several
OL,9,Fofficers have talked of taking
OL,10,FCreswell at face value. They are
OL,11,Ftrained police officers who should
OL,12,Fhave set about satisfying themselves
OL,13,Fthat this was a non-suspicious
OL,14,Fdeath...red flags were ignored.
OL,16,F"This is in part due to a lack of
OL,17,Fexperience with one constable
OL,18,Fattending the scene "six days out of
OL,19,Ftraining."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
