OL,3,CKatie Simpson Ombudsman report
OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FThe prosecution claimed Crewsell was
OL,7,Fin an illicit relationship with the
OL,8,Fyoung women and he strangled her out
OL,9,Fof jealously and then tried to cover
OL,10,Fhis tracks by making her death look
OL,11,Flike suicide.
OL,13,FSomething police believed at the time.
OL,15,FIn 2010 the former jockey was jailed
OL,16,Ffor six months after pleading guilty
OL,17,Fto assaulting an ex girlfriend.
OL,19,FComplaints were made against 18
OL,20,Fofficers ranging in rank from
OL,21,FConstable to Detective Chief Inspector.
