OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FIn a statement the PSNI said: "The
OL,7,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland can
OL,8,Fconfirm that we have received an
OL,9,Finvestigation file from the Office of
OL,10,Fthe Police Ombudsman, which is
OL,11,Fcurrently being considered. It would
OL,12,Ftherefore be inappropriate to make any
OL,13,Ffurther comment at this time."
