OL,3,CKatie Simpson Ombudsman report
OL,4,Chighlights 'red flags ignored'
OL,6,FThe Police Ombudsman said: "Given that
OL,7,Fdisciplinary-related processes have
OL,8,Fnot yet concluded and, as a result, we
OL,9,Fhave not yet been able to communicate
OL,10,Four findings and the outcome of our
OL,11,Finvestigation with Katie's family, it
OL,12,Fis concerning that details of our
OL,13,Fmisconduct file would now appear to be
OL,14,Fin the public domain. In this context
OL,15,Fit would be inappropriate for us to
OL,16,Fmake any comment."
